"ng icons na kumakatawan sa istado ng keyboard."

#. (itstool) path: sect1/para
#: C/index.docbook:161
msgid ""
"The <application>Keyboard Accessibility Monitor</application> shows you the "
"status of the keyboard accessibility features when these are in use. For "
"example, you can see which modifier keys are currently active, and which "
"mouse buttons are being pressed via the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Ipinapakita ng Keyboard Accessibility Monitor ang estado ng mga "
"accessibility features ng keyboard habang ginagamit ang mga ito. Halimbawa, "
"maaari mong makita kung anong modifier keys ang kasalukuyang gumagana at "
"kung anong mouse buttons ang kasalakuyang pinapagana sa pamamagitan ng "
"keyboard."

#. (itstool) path: sect1/para
#: C/index.docbook:163
msgid ""
"For more on using keyboard accessibility features, see the <ulink "
"url=\"help:mate-access-guide\">Desktop Accessibility Guide</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Para malaman ang higit pa sa paggamit ng keyboard accessibility features, "
"mangyaring tignan ang Gabay sa Desktop Accessibility."

